85
00:05:38,600 --> 00:05:39,160
Very well.

86
00:05:39,839 --> 00:05:41,439
You'll all follow my command later.

87
00:05:41,959 --> 00:05:43,399
These are from the Nine Heavens.

88
00:05:43,920 --> 00:05:45,279
They naturally obey my orders.

89
00:05:58,399 --> 00:05:59,000
