238
00:15:19,580 --> 00:15:20,419
Do you like it?

239
00:15:27,120 --> 00:15:28,200
I have a question.

240
00:15:29,139 --> 00:15:30,340
You've asked everything.

241
00:15:33,340 --> 00:15:34,539
You're not the Night Deity.

242
00:15:36,100 --> 00:15:37,580
You didn't kill my mother.

243
00:15:37,919 --> 00:15:38,480
Right?

244
00:15:50,580 --> 00:15:50,940
Look.

245
00:15:52,220 --> 00:15:52,820
A falling star.

246
00:15:56,580 --> 00:15:57,659
Don't change the subject.

247
00:16:01,179 --> 00:16:02,580
Come sit with me for a while.

248
00:16:03,820 --> 00:16:04,419
Okay?

249
00:16:19,179 --> 00:16:19,980
I'm really happy.

250
00:16:24,100 --> 00:16:26,440
I've been sitting here
for over 1,000 years.

251
00:16:27,360 --> 00:16:28,600
Having you by my side

252
00:16:29,580 --> 00:16:30,340
makes me glad.

253
00:16:34,700 --> 00:16:35,980
You're acting strange today.

254
00:16:45,279 --> 00:16:46,200
Fireflies.

255
00:16:54,980 --> 00:16:56,299
These are your doing?

256
00:16:57,059 --> 00:16:57,580
No.

257
00:17:00,512 --> 00:17:03,727
♪Searching through half a lifetime,
I rest with the breeze as my pillow♪

258
00:17:03,727 --> 00:17:06,237
♪The bright moon's yearning
echoes through lonely strings♪

259
00:17:07,160 --> 00:17:08,676
♪Gazing across the mortal realm♪

260
00:17:08,676 --> 00:17:12,135
♪She appears where lanterns fade♪

261
00:17:13,444 --> 00:17:16,610
♪Storms disperse.
Drunken reunions trace past bonds♪

262
00:17:16,610 --> 00:17:19,300
♪Asking when we'll meet in another life♪

263
00:17:19,744 --> 00:17:22,884
♪A millennium passes in moments.
Where's today's joy♪

264
00:17:22,884 --> 00:17:25,732
♪This love defies severing♪

265
00:17:25,732 --> 00:17:28,432
♪Cutting a fragment of time♪

266
00:17:28,432 --> 00:17:32,554
♪Shattered stars can't compare
to my resolve with you♪

267
00:17:32,554 --> 00:17:38,291
♪Though countless sorrows
may fall like petals♪

268
00:17:38,692 --> 00:17:41,352
♪For this stretch of time♪

269
00:17:41,352 --> 00:17:45,649
♪Walk with you through life and death♪

270
00:17:45,649 --> 00:17:47,812
♪Carving your essence in my heart♪

271
00:17:47,812 --> 00:17:52,164
♪Creating life's fairest memory♪

272
00:17:54,299 --> 00:17:55,259
Ye Chenyuan.

273
00:17:57,200 --> 00:17:58,440
If I am the Night Deity,

274
00:17:59,759 --> 00:18:01,079
will you insist on killing me

275
00:18:02,480 --> 00:18:03,759
like you vowed before?

276
00:18:08,880 --> 00:18:10,400
I'll find a way to prove

277
00:18:11,359 --> 00:18:12,640
you're not the Night Deity.

278
00:18:40,660 --> 00:18:41,460
Ye Chenyuan.

279
00:18:43,460 --> 00:18:44,259
Ye Chenyuan.

280
00:19:00,900 --> 00:19:01,859
Ye Chenyuan.

281
00:19:02,740 --> 00:19:04,460
Did you really leave like this?

282
00:19:14,700 --> 00:19:16,380
The Divine Sword is unsealed.

283
00:19:17,539 --> 00:19:20,099
Sword Master, please claim it.

284
00:19:52,180 --> 00:19:53,380
Congratulations, Sword Master.

285
00:19:53,579 --> 00:19:55,700
- The sword is unsealed!
- The sword is unsealed!

286
00:20:09,940 --> 00:20:10,779
Night Deity's power.

287
00:20:11,140 --> 00:20:12,099
Stay vigilant!

288
00:20:23,779 --> 00:20:25,500
If any of you use spiritual power,

289
00:20:26,420 --> 00:20:27,859
you'll die instantly.

290
00:20:31,740 --> 00:20:32,339
Everyone,

291
00:20:32,619 --> 00:20:33,779
form purification formations!

292
00:20:40,460 --> 00:20:41,280
What are you doing?

293
00:20:44,740 --> 00:20:45,380
Bai Xiaoying!

294
00:20:45,819 --> 00:20:47,460
You've been colluding with Ye Chenyuan!

295
00:20:47,660 --> 00:20:48,779
I knew you...

296
00:20:51,980 --> 00:20:53,019
Keep talking nonsense,

297
00:20:54,019 --> 00:20:55,420
and I'll rip your mouth apart.

298
00:20:56,180 --> 00:20:57,019
Ye Chenyuan,

299
00:20:57,380 --> 00:20:59,059
I failed to teach my girl well.

300
00:20:59,619 --> 00:21:00,660
Wanyan's mistakes

301
00:21:00,819 --> 00:21:01,900
are my failures.

302
00:21:04,579 --> 00:21:05,380
You said

303
00:21:06,420 --> 00:21:07,579
if I were the Night Deity,

304
00:21:08,259 --> 00:21:09,299
you wouldn't kill me.

305
00:21:09,940 --> 00:21:11,900
You'd find evidence to prove I was not.

306
00:21:15,339 --> 00:21:15,940
Exactly.

307
00:21:17,299 --> 00:21:18,539
Because I know you're not.

308
00:21:19,420 --> 00:21:20,539
You're too naive.

309
00:21:21,339 --> 00:21:22,140
So...

310
00:21:23,619 --> 00:21:25,579
don't blame me for showing no mercy.

311
00:21:38,160 --> 00:21:40,759
You didn't really think
I was helping you purge residual toxins?

312
00:21:42,720 --> 00:21:44,319
I was injecting the Night Clan poison

313
00:21:45,119 --> 00:21:46,480
into your body.

314
00:21:58,180 --> 00:21:58,940
Impossible.

315
00:22:00,460 --> 00:22:01,140
I don't believe.

316
00:22:01,500 --> 00:22:03,579
After I came to the Nine Heavens
half a year ago,

317
00:22:04,339 --> 00:22:05,339
my sole purpose

318
00:22:05,460 --> 00:22:06,579
was to seize the sword.

319
00:22:07,460 --> 00:22:09,579
Everything I've done led to this moment.

320
00:22:11,460 --> 00:22:13,180
And now, you've finally handed it to me.

321
00:22:29,140 --> 00:22:30,180
Are you saying,

322
00:22:31,619 --> 00:22:32,779
this whole time,

323
00:22:34,619 --> 00:22:35,740
you've been lying to me?

324
00:22:41,259 --> 00:22:42,140
No.

325
00:22:43,180 --> 00:22:45,059
Why didn't you seize the sword earlier

326
00:22:45,460 --> 00:22:46,700
but help me get the crystal?

327
00:22:46,740 --> 00:22:47,700
Because

328
00:22:48,259 --> 00:22:50,779
I needed the Sword Master
to unseal it for me.

329
00:22:56,259 --> 00:22:57,500
Stop joking.

330
00:22:58,700 --> 00:23:00,460
I won't fall for this.

331
00:23:02,319 --> 00:23:03,400
What's really going on?

332
00:23:08,420 --> 00:23:09,539
Give me the sword first.

333
00:23:10,740 --> 00:23:12,059
Whatever the problem is,

334
00:23:12,819 --> 00:23:14,500
we'll solve it together.

335
00:23:14,819 --> 00:23:15,460
Okay?

336
00:23:16,099 --> 00:23:17,339
My problem is,

337
00:23:18,140 --> 00:23:21,660
I intended to use you to reclaim my clan
and obtain the sword crystal.

338
00:23:22,740 --> 00:23:25,259
I never imagined
you'd help me so wholeheartedly,

339
00:23:26,019 --> 00:23:27,619
even bringing along your master.

340
00:23:28,079 --> 00:23:30,000
I truly don't know how to thank you.

341
00:23:39,900 --> 00:23:40,660
Ye Chenyuan,

342
00:23:42,059 --> 00:23:44,339
I don't care what excuses
or compulsions you have.

343
00:23:45,420 --> 00:23:47,380
If you don't return
the Divine Sword now,

344
00:23:47,900 --> 00:23:49,619
no explanation you give in the future

345
00:23:50,259 --> 00:23:51,819
will ever make me forgive you!

346
00:23:58,359 --> 00:23:59,319
Forgive me?

347
00:24:00,480 --> 00:24:01,839
Seems you've truly gone mad.

348
00:24:02,559 --> 00:24:04,559
You didn't really think
I fell in love with you?

349
00:24:06,656 --> 00:24:10,119
♪Drunken delusions feed this obsession♪

350
00:24:10,119 --> 00:24:10,920
No.

351
00:24:12,839 --> 00:24:14,519
You were
under the Truthwater's influence.

352
00:24:15,720 --> 00:24:17,440
Your words couldn't be false.

353
00:24:18,119 --> 00:24:19,440
Don't flatter yourself.

354
00:24:20,799 --> 00:24:21,519
I never

355
00:24:22,680 --> 00:24:24,319
fell for you.

356
00:24:25,152 --> 00:24:32,234
♪How could I seek you in fading lights?♪

357
00:24:34,079 --> 00:24:35,319
Your current expression

358
00:24:36,160 --> 00:24:37,400
is truly remarkable.

359
00:24:38,920 --> 00:24:40,440
Your remaining life

360
00:24:41,960 --> 00:24:43,880
will be taken away
by the lingering poison.

361
00:24:48,980 --> 00:24:49,779
Ye Chenyuan!

362
00:24:55,579 --> 00:24:56,099
Xiaoying.

363
00:24:57,500 --> 00:24:58,339
How are you feeling?

364
00:25:24,980 --> 00:25:26,619
The sword injury missed vital points.

365
00:25:26,859 --> 00:25:28,500
I've purged the residual toxins.

366
00:25:29,099 --> 00:25:30,700
Her severe injuries at the Cloud Summit

367
00:25:30,859 --> 00:25:32,140
resulted mostly

368
00:25:32,299 --> 00:25:33,579
from a mental blow.

369
00:25:34,299 --> 00:25:35,500
She's stable now.

370
00:25:35,859 --> 00:25:36,900
I'll go prepare medicine.

371
00:25:37,500 --> 00:25:37,900
Alright.

372
00:25:38,259 --> 00:25:38,900
Go.

373
00:25:46,099 --> 00:25:47,180
Bai Xiaoying,

374
00:25:48,099 --> 00:25:50,220
as the Sword Master of the Nine Heavens,

375
00:25:51,259 --> 00:25:53,940
you've repeatedly spared Ye Chenyuan.

376
00:25:55,059 --> 00:25:56,740
This time, you committed a grave error,

377
00:25:57,299 --> 00:25:58,660
letting the sword be taken!

378
00:25:59,859 --> 00:26:01,259
I would like to know

379
00:26:01,980 --> 00:26:04,019
what explanation you would offer.

380
00:26:05,299 --> 00:26:06,059
My lord,

381
00:26:07,779 --> 00:26:10,059
I was deceived by Ye Chenyuan, causing

382
00:26:10,819 --> 00:26:11,740
the sword's loss

383
00:26:12,779 --> 00:26:13,779
and implicating our sect.

384
00:26:14,539 --> 00:26:15,900
I willingly accept punishment.

385
00:26:17,779 --> 00:26:19,099
But the Cloud Summit battle

386
00:26:19,660 --> 00:26:20,660
was suspicious.

387
00:26:21,339 --> 00:26:22,700
Ye Chenyuan isn't the Night Deity.

388
00:26:23,259 --> 00:26:24,140
May I be permitted

389
00:26:24,660 --> 00:26:25,819
to go to the Night Clan

390
00:26:26,059 --> 00:26:26,940
for investigation?

391
00:26:27,019 --> 00:26:28,660
Even at this juncture,

392
00:26:29,059 --> 00:26:30,180
you still defend him?

393
00:26:30,940 --> 00:26:32,579
Have you really developed feelings

394
00:26:33,059 --> 00:26:34,339
for Ye Chenyuan?

395
00:26:37,579 --> 00:26:38,940
I'm not defending him.

396
00:26:40,140 --> 00:26:40,700
My lord,

397
00:26:42,660 --> 00:26:43,819
Xiaoying acted foolishly,

398
00:26:44,579 --> 00:26:45,779
but she was deceived

399
00:26:45,779 --> 00:26:46,700
by Ye Chenyuan.

400
00:26:47,420 --> 00:26:48,579
She's hurt in mind and soul.

401
00:26:49,220 --> 00:26:50,779
She shouldn't contact him anymore.

402
00:26:51,700 --> 00:26:53,180
I request permission to go

403
00:26:54,059 --> 00:26:54,980
to reclaim the sword

404
00:26:55,180 --> 00:26:56,059
for the Nine Heavens!

405
00:26:56,660 --> 00:26:57,380
Master,

406
00:26:57,700 --> 00:26:58,539
don't!

407
00:26:58,660 --> 00:26:59,099
Enough!

408
00:27:03,299 --> 00:27:04,819
This matter is assigned to you.

409
00:27:06,099 --> 00:27:07,380
I've received word

410
00:27:07,940 --> 00:27:09,500
that Ye Chenyuan has announced

411
00:27:10,420 --> 00:27:11,980
his upcoming marriage to Hua Yuying.

412
00:27:12,460 --> 00:27:15,859
Use this chance
to recover the Divine Sword.

413
00:27:17,539 --> 00:27:18,900
As for you, Bai Xiaoying,

414
00:27:20,339 --> 00:27:22,140
you're grounded in this Huiyue Abode

415
00:27:23,099 --> 00:27:24,420
for self-reflection.

416
00:27:35,859 --> 00:27:37,099
He and Hua Yuying

417
00:27:38,539 --> 00:27:39,339
are getting married?

418
00:27:55,980 --> 00:27:56,900
Ye Chenyuan.

419
00:27:58,380 --> 00:27:59,259
Ye Chenyuan.

420
00:27:59,859 --> 00:28:00,420
No!

421
00:28:20,519 --> 00:28:22,400
Why did things come to this?

422
00:28:23,559 --> 00:28:24,200
Do you know...

423
00:28:25,079 --> 00:28:26,480
You asked me to marry Hua Yuying.

424
00:28:28,319 --> 00:28:29,200
It broke my heart.

425
00:28:32,736 --> 00:28:34,176
Do you have feelings for Xiaoying?

426
00:28:36,160 --> 00:28:36,720
Yes.

427
00:28:43,380 --> 00:28:44,619
Don't flatter yourself.

428
00:28:45,220 --> 00:28:46,099
I never

429
00:28:47,019 --> 00:28:48,619
fell for you.

430
00:28:52,460 --> 00:28:53,619
Ye Chenyuan,

431
00:28:54,980 --> 00:28:57,180
do I really look that easy to fool?

432
00:29:10,539 --> 00:29:11,220
Master!

433
00:29:12,059 --> 00:29:13,380
Are you here to see Xiaoying?

434
00:29:16,900 --> 00:29:17,539
Yes.

435
00:29:18,019 --> 00:29:19,980
I'll go to reclaim the sword
from the Night Clan.

436
00:29:20,579 --> 00:29:21,339
I'm concerned

437
00:29:21,619 --> 00:29:22,539
and came to check.

438
00:29:22,819 --> 00:29:23,500
But...

439
00:29:23,940 --> 00:29:26,059
Xiaoying's already resting.

440
00:29:26,420 --> 00:29:27,940
You could tell me your message

441
00:29:28,140 --> 00:29:29,380
for relay later.

442
00:29:32,420 --> 00:29:33,180
Chang Qingrou,

443
00:29:34,099 --> 00:29:35,579
are you hiding something from me?

444
00:29:36,539 --> 00:29:37,019
I...

445
00:29:37,619 --> 00:29:38,180
I...

446
00:29:41,420 --> 00:29:42,299
Where's Xiaoying?

447
00:29:43,660 --> 00:29:44,579
Master,

448
00:29:44,980 --> 00:29:45,980
I couldn't stop her.

449
00:29:46,059 --> 00:29:47,539
She left at dawn.

450
00:29:49,259 --> 00:29:50,819
Must be for Ye Chenyuan's wedding.

451
00:29:51,660 --> 00:29:52,579
I'll go bring her back.

452
00:30:27,900 --> 00:30:28,420
Who's there?

453
00:30:30,339 --> 00:30:31,180
Where is Ye Chenyuan?

454
00:30:31,740 --> 00:30:32,740
I need to talk to him.

455
00:30:33,500 --> 00:30:35,619
Today is the wedding day
of the Lord and Hua Yuying.

456
00:30:35,900 --> 00:30:37,019
No outsiders are welcome.

457
00:30:42,700 --> 00:30:44,299
Looks like I came in time.

458
00:30:44,859 --> 00:30:46,259
How could this joyous event

459
00:30:46,900 --> 00:30:48,380
be without me?

460
00:30:59,043 --> 00:31:01,797
♪Withered trees bear decaying rings♪

461
00:31:02,499 --> 00:31:05,411
♪Love and hate entwine in cycles♪

462
00:31:06,168 --> 00:31:08,978
♪Vows unravel into parting words♪

463
00:31:09,624 --> 00:31:12,582
♪The harsh mortal world
cuts like a blade♪

464
00:31:13,155 --> 00:31:16,137
♪Your icy tone♪

465
00:31:16,547 --> 00:31:19,672
♪Wounds across lifetimes♪

466
00:31:20,291 --> 00:31:22,861
♪The bitterest tear stains♪

467
00:31:22,861 --> 00:31:26,659
♪Scorch my lips♪

468
00:31:27,331 --> 00:31:30,137
♪Memories pile up, tender and warm♪

469
00:31:30,819 --> 00:31:33,670
♪Our fated bond clings unyielding♪

470
00:31:34,371 --> 00:31:37,329
♪Fate's mottled lines on palms♪

471
00:31:37,923 --> 00:31:41,187
♪Severing dawn from endless night♪

472
00:31:41,187 --> 00:31:46,083
♪Bitter winds gather sparse stars♪

473
00:31:46,083 --> 00:31:48,611
♪Yet still I wait♪

474
00:31:48,611 --> 00:31:55,828
♪For a promise lost,
to share life's journey♪

475
00:31:55,870 --> 00:31:58,627
♪Ephemeral blooms fade overnight♪

476
00:31:58,627 --> 00:32:02,915
♪Drunken delusions feed this obsession♪

477
00:32:03,119 --> 00:32:08,579
♪Through lifetimes of chains,
only my sighs remain♪

478
00:32:09,865 --> 00:32:13,635
♪Sorrow soars over peaks♪

479
00:32:13,635 --> 00:32:17,123
♪Never reaching the far shore♪

480
